## OpenRouter API Key Setup
# 1. Sign up at https://openrouter.ai
# 2. Get free API key from https://openrouter.ai/keys
# 3. Copy this file to .env and uncomment/add your key

# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Usage:
# Windows CMD: set OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-yourkey
# PowerShell: $env:OPENROUTER_API_KEY="sk-or-v1-yourkey"
# Bash: export OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-yourkey
# Or use python-dotenv: pip install python-dotenv && load_dotenv()
